  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>TVI PTE LTD is a rapidly expanding Singapore based company with an extensive European and French network of direct Farm produce to Asia. The team comprises passionate and dedicated staff whose first love is fresh produce and the European traditional agriculture evolved with modern farming methods and technology that is environmentally sustainable and yet authentic to its original European roots. We are the sole agents in Asia for a couple of leading Fresh produce brands in France and Europe. We invite likeminded individuals who have the flair and passion for retail but also with the passion to see European fresh produce to Asia, to apply to be part of the exciting and dynamic team.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>[No job summary was provided in the original JD.]</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Drive demand planning by analyzing supermarket industry trends to optimize inventory and sales forecasting</li><li>Lead and manage a team of van sales drivers to consistently meet weekly and monthly sales targets</li><li>Operate a chiller truck to maintain delivery continuity during team members’ leave or absence</li><li>Communicate fluently in Mandarin and English to coordinate with team members and stakeholders effectively</li><li>Resolve operational issues on the ground promptly to support the sales team and escalate to sales management when necessary</li><li>Lead the sales team by setting clear objectives and motivating members to achieve sales results</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Possess a valid Singapore Class 3 Manual driving license held for over one year</li></ul>",
